{"tid":60691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一月頭去台北問題","createTime":"2016-12-30T15:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T14:03:52.000Z","uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9500b658b2faea291727e50dbd650460974995f9","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:43:50.000Z","msg":"第一次去旅行 <br />\n編左台証<br />\n兩個人5日4夜 40000台幣夠唔夠<br />\n有咩要注意 <br />\n用expedia訂野"},{"pid":"b9e0ac49c74974f1d0e4189eb08d9152803fd34c","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924aa96b3f78b2f0582e5e65bcf526a124e1c20e","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867ebc86e9bfd650d1eb86e72da34fca2015ed83","tid":60691,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去旅行 <br />\n編左台証<br />\n兩個人5日4夜 40000台幣夠唔夠<br />\n有咩要注意 <br />\n用expedia訂野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好偷海鮮入廁所食<br />\n<br />\n利申：去過6次台灣"},{"pid":"be442b48f80b272fbe3a80655c4c79d7ebc07d8a","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有呢"},{"pid":"5c100ff47c5033a9890959258351b3eeea575b06","tid":60691,"uid":26345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T15:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一次去旅行 <br />\n編左台証<br />\n兩個人5日4夜 40000台幣夠唔夠<br />\n有咩要注意 <br />\n用expedia訂野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真<br />\n1.台證要用雙面白 a4紙<br />\n2.睇清楚一號定二號航廈（for 桃園機場）<br />\n3.去西門町有後生用國語問你係咪台北人，唔好理佢行走就得<br />\n4.40000台絕對夠用，一餐普通韓燒500台左右，居酒屋就1500台，日式高級放題（eg上引)2000台左右，你唔係日日食貴野就一定夠<br />\n5.台灣（台北）10點左右大部分店都閂門，要食野買野請早<br />\n6.護照跟身，身分證去到台灣冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁，有野想問先再答你"},{"pid":"0def90dac3171e5b00f21f67d8cd36d6cd2ca09f","tid":60691,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:02:09.000Z","msg":"去台灣唔洗太緊張，始終溝通上冇咩大問題，文化接近。<br />\n最重要尊重當地的所有野。<br />\n40000，睇你用途係咩？不過多數就肯定夠用。我20000去5日仲有剩。<br />\n祝開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0ceb7f3cb92479bc7d5383328c99911df5bc6e","tid":60691,"uid":4665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"我兩個人6日5夜都係用左20000台幣 仲要中間有時搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ed5148048fef9ecb1fc3cae651f12b592e68d8","tid":60691,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:36:34.000Z","msg":"4萬好夠洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我去台北8日7夜都係用4500住宿酒店4500買野食野<br />\n入台證同護照要長期跟身，你買電話卡(預付卡)同兌換台仔都要出示呢兩樣野，佢地對呢d政策好嚴格，唔似香港話買就買，台灣要實名認證。<br />\n夜市千奇唔好食骰子牛/雜腸<br />\n淡水千奇唔好食超長雪糕<br />\n有唔清楚再問"},{"pid":"e8ea0891d920c1715db11ab1f019ae22db77f0de","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:00:54.000Z","msg":"己經開左海外提款 係咪應該帶番少少港幣係身 <br />\n有信用卡."},{"pid":"581fb5b4de12b4b18980aecf647e77f604fa8abf","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f9e285cbd0a9eb64d9c5777166d00281065c5b","tid":60691,"uid":761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e2431b9140a9a25f213ca0e8e011c6c1aa4c8b","tid":60691,"uid":8439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T14:03:52.000Z","msg":"西門町有人行埋黎話自己係乜乜大學 乜乜學生 叫你幫手買野即走唔洗理佢"}]}